name: MOO Burger
directions: Building is a white building on a slight hill. They have an outdoor seating area. There is an incline to actually get into the building but there is a ramp for accessibility. There are also steps. Small burger place, it’s on your right when you come in there is only one bathroom, it is a single stall and gender neutral. Completely gender neutral and uses it also very clean.
comment: You probably should order something to use the bathroom in this place. However, the place is very LGBT friendly and especially transgender friendly. The whole area practically is. If you go in and ask to use a safe a bathroom they’ll understand. I’ve been going there as a safe place for awhile now. Very friendly people, they’ll get it.
